doc.title: Isishwankathelo seNxulumaniso Vula Ngolwandiso
doc.description:
Olu lwandiso lukuvumela ukuba ulawule ngokulula ukuba ihyperlink ivulwa njani.

Ifestile: ezinye iibhrawuza, iifestile ezizivelelayo, iifestile ezintsha, iifestile ezintsha ze-incognito, ifestile yangoku (ehlala ikho)

Iithebhu: ekhohlo kwithebhu yangoku, ithebhu yangoku, ekunene kwethebhu yangoku (ehlala ikho)

Imo esebenzayo: ayisebenzi, yivule ngoko nangoko (ngokungagqibekanga)
